These avatars are the default avatars featured by VRChat, located in the Public row of the Avatars page in the [[Special:MyLanguage/Main Menu|Main Menu]]. The vast majority of Public Avatars featured here are from VRChat themselves or the winners of the following [[Special:MyLanguage/Events#World and avatar Jams|Jams]]: [[Special:MyLanguage/Avatars for Everyone|Avatars for Everyone]], and [[Special:MyLanguage/Summer Festival Jam 2025#Jam winners|Summer Festival Jam 2025]].